<body>
	<div class="container">
	
		<<@@ $navbar @@>>
		<div class="well">
			<div class="content">
				<div id="helpWizard">
					<h3>Step 1</h3>
					<section>
						<p>Download the Excel File - Custom or Sample Excel File from the <i>"Download Sample"</i> link on top of the page : </p>
						<p><span class="badge">Simple Excel</span> Includes very basic options to create CTP based design.</p>
						<p><span class="badge">Custom Excel</span> Includes advanced CTP properties to create customized CTP design.</p>
						<div class="well">
							<img class="img-responsive img-thumbnail" src="/SCL/images/Step1.jpg" alt="Step1">
						</div>
					</section>
					<h3>Step 2</h3>
					<section>
						<p>Fill in the required data in the downloaded Excel. Columns highlighted in <font color="orange">Orange</font> in the Excel are mandatory to be filled.</p>
						<p>Brief description for the Excel worksheets is as below</p>
						<p><span class="badge">Networksheet</span> <span class="badge">Sites</span> <span class="badge">Sides</span> <span class="badge">Duct-details</span> <span class="badge">Demands</span>
						<div class="well">
							<img class="img-responsive img-thumbnail" src="/SCL/images/Step2.jpg" alt="Step2">
						</div>
					</section>
					<h3>Step 3</h3>
					<section>
						<p>Browse to the above filled-in Excel File, select the option to generate the mpz file or generate the CTP supported Script and Command Line Excel File and Submit the same.</p>
						<div class="well">
							<img class="img-responsive" src="/SCL/images/Step3.jpg" alt="Step3">
						</div>
					</section>
					<h3>Step 4</h3>
					<section>
						<p>Post submission, the Excel is vaidated. Once validated, if there are issues re-upload the file. Mentioned below are the FAIL/SUCCESS scenarios on upoading the file.</p>
						<div class="well">
							<img class="img-responsive img-thumbnail" src="/SCL/images/Step4.jpg" alt="Step4">
						</div>
					</section>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

